ents Need One?"> <div class="ArticleImageContainer"> <img class="ArticleImage" src="//storage-prtl-co.imgix.net/endor/articles/379/images/1540540737_rawpixel-617400-unsplash.jpg?h=180&amp;w=263.33333333333&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format&amp;q=40" alt="What Is a Transcript of Records and When Do Students Need One?" loading="lazy" width="263" height="180"> </div> <div class="ArticleName"> <span class="ArticleNameHolder">What Is a Transcript of Records and When Do Students Need One?</span> </div> </a> </figure>  <figure class="RelatedArticle"> <a class="ArticleAnchor" href="https://www.mastersportal.com/articles/345/the-complete-guide-to-english-language-certificates.html" target="_blank" title="The Complete Guide to English-Language Certificates"> <div class="ArticleImageContainer"> <img class="ArticleImage" src="//storage-prtl-co.imgix.net/endor/articles/345/images/1540552596_freestocks-org-65291-unsplash.jpg?h=180&amp;w=263.33333333333&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format&amp;q=40" alt="The Complete Guide to English-Language Certificates" loading="lazy" width="263" height="180"> </div> <div class="ArticleName"> <span class="ArticleNameHolder">The Complete Guide to English-Language Certificates</span> </div> </a> </figure>  <figure class="RelatedArticle"> <a class="ArticleAnchor" href="https://www.mastersportal.com/articles/1894/how-to-write-a-scholarship-essay-that-will-impress-the-admission-committee.html" target="_blank" title="How to Write a Scholarship Essay that Will Impress the Admission Committee"> <div class="ArticleImageContainer"> <img class="ArticleImage" src="//storage-prtl-co.imgix.net/endor/articles/1894/images/1541607621_shutterstock_210056155.jpg?h=180&amp;w=263.33333333333&amp;fit=crop&amp;crop=faces&amp;auto=format&amp;q=40" alt="How to Write a Scholarship Essay that Will Impress the Admission Committee" loading="lazy" width="263" height="180"> </div> <div class="ArticleName"> <span class="ArticleNameHolder">How to Write a Schol