"NavigatorButton" data-name="PersonalityTest" data-url="/personality-test/" > Check which discipline fits me </button> </li> <li> <button class="NavigatorButton" data-name="CountryTest" data-open="tab" data-url="/country-test/" > Check which country fits me </button> </li> <li class="DesktopOnlyBlock"> <button class="NavigatorButton js-tipsListSearchTip" data-name="Search" data-url="//#portal_name#portal.com/search/#sblp#" data-open="current"> Search all #portal_name# </button> </li> </ul>  </div> </div> </div>  </div>  <div data-module="" class="Module StudyPortals_Shared_Modules_StructuredData_RenderStructuredDataModule">  <script type="application/ld+json"> {
